snippet.title: 🐱Dashero: Archer, Sword & Magic trailer - Android & iOS Download Now!
snippet.description:
Android & iOS - Pre-Order is ready now!
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.trefle.dashero
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1504030024

With only a sword and magic in your hand, you will face a fantasy world full of monsters. 
Explore and adventure through various mazes, and challenge hundreds of dangerous monsters and big bosses. For survival, you can obtain different random skills and combine them for have countless possibilities.
 
Create unique fighting styles to break through all the challenges! 

Game features: 
1. Slash attack and long-range magic to defeat different enemies 
2. Fantastic and gorgeous 3D world design 
3. Super spectcular battle effects and fights against strange creatures - such as banana monsters!  
4. Beautiful and eye-catching character design with unique special combat skills
